title: NFL ATL: Week 16 preview
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 16 preview
description:
A room full of heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling -- preview Week 16 action.  Which teams will take a giant leap toward the playoffs?  Did Kevin Patra survive Monday night's drama in Detroit?  Is "Wes" safe from his softball pants? There’s only one place to find out.  Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL and help the heroes by nominating them for the 2013 Stitcher Awards at stitcher.promotw.com

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
